description: Illustrator Nathan St John and writer Ben Wagner bring modern noir to the West in the original graphic novel Baja. In this sexy, twisting thriller, Hil and Zack - a beautiful woman and a man who knows better - must escape a stalker whose fate is tied to their own. St John and Wagner play with conventions, leading readers in unexpected directions with a story that deftly weaves two tales of love, sex, greed, and betrayal. St John's distinctive art style perfectly matches the shadowy criminal world of Baja.
name: Baja - Heroes, Villians, And Everyone Between

description: Veronica in 'Not So Clothes-Minded!' In order to break Veronica's habit of arriving late for class, Mr. Weatherbee sentences her to community service! Intent on helping the struggling thrift store she's been forced to aide, Ronnie utilizes her fashion sense for good in a way nobody thought possible! Can the conceited socialite make a difference and learn a lesson in the process? Betty in 'Triangle Wrangle' Trying to secure a summer job, Betty turns to Lodge Land where Archie and Adam are working as rival vampires! But will the boys' antics vying for Betty's affections help or hinder her job hunt?

A retro and visionary science fiction saga! Ecumenopolis - a futuristic metropolis where the bodies disappear, a city whose foundations are undermined by an internal threat. A civil war between castes, and Black Eightball, Aristoi, Cives, Bodysnatchers, shamans, and White Eightball.

Route de Masions Rouges is a sexy and surreal satirical comedy set in a fantasy world's Parisian neighborhood. It's quite crowded with five brothels competing for control. These hot and hot-headed tenants are caught up in a five-way battle to make their own Maison the most powerful of all. Yet it's all fun and games until the slimy mayor enters the picture - and then the girls might have found a common enemy big enough for them to forget their feud and work together.

Demons invade the Carnival at Venice, horrible nightmare-reflections of beloved fairytales characters, determined to tear a permanent hole from their twisted world to ours. Demon Hunter Gabriel must force the demoness Cinderella, monster Little Mermaid, and countless others back through the portal before the last night of Carnival, or no one will live happily ever after.

The hot new series that redefines the horror genre concludes here!!! When a man wakes up to find that the world around him has begun to forget him one by one he will have to discover the source of the curse that threatens to erase his very existence before it's too late. Meanwhile, a detective is closing in on the secret of the Theater and with the existence of the killers about to be revealed the family of psychopaths will be forced to make a decision that could very well threaten the entire world. From the writer and creator of The Waking and FLY comes a horror series brought to you by the company that does horror right. Featuring over 27 pages of content!

description: Hakata Soy is new at Astronaut Academy, and things aren't going well for him so far. How will he find time to study for his classes in Fire Throwing, Anti-Gravity Gymnastics, and Wearing Cute Hats when there's a robot doppelganger on its way to kill him?
name: Zero Gravity

person_credits.role: writer, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover

description: Autumn's unpredictable magic clashes with Schizandra's purported powers as village protectionist. All is not as it seems. On their way out of the village, Autumn and her squirrel, Widdershin, encounter three village beauties, and Autumn tells tales. How far will the unwitting beauties push Autumn? Then it's off into the Black Wood to find the reclusive Splinter, who lives in a house set high in a tree. Splinter is a collector of mushrooms, pods, and other plantlife. What will he reveal to the captivated Autumn, and what tales will she tell him? Later, in the dark of night, while Autumn lies in her darkened bedroom in Schizandra's house, a startling message comes from deep inside the Black Wood.

volume.name: Walt Disney The Miracle of the White Stallions
Annie Sprinkle in the Adventures of Miss Timed

description: Here's what we can tell you: Tom Judge and his companion, clairvoyant Tilly Grimes have discovered something is wrong with the world. Their discovery has prompted them to embark on a mission to track down the bearers of the 13 Artifacts. But isn't that what caused problems the last time?
name: New Creation, Part 3

description: As the snow begins to melt and the harshest winter in Marshville's history comes to a close, the towns people begin to dig themselves out with a new hope. But even as everybody celebrates their good fortune, a bigger and even deadlier threat descends upon their isolated town. Somewhere in the wilderness surrounding Marshville lurks a creature of unnatural ferocity and power. Rumors spread of the creature being a werewolf. As the frozen snows recede, the countless bones of the creatures previous victims begin to reveal themselves. If Meriem can't destroy the monster, the future of Marshville looks bleak.

With the true identity of the werewolf revealed, Meriem must now come to a decision. Should she track the creature down and destroy it, or with help, capture the monster and attempt to cure the human locked within it? Meriem's choice could have grave consequences for Marshville's inhabitants!
ORION PAX -- the 'bot who will someday be Optimus Prime -- lies defeated. Cybertron is in flames. ZETA PRIME is poised to conquer all. Does any hope remain -- or is this a very short chapter?
name: Choices

description: Who knows what 'steam pipe dreams' lurk within the hearts of men? We know...and now we'll share with you some of the most intriguing, elucidating sketches from the minds of our top artist-adventurers! Where might these glimpses into other worlds lead? That, only time will tell!
name: Sketchbook

description: Once upon a time, there were several refined ladies who went to the finest finishing schools, and they were all assigned very dull duties in high society...but I took them away from all that, and now they work for me. Now they live lives of high adventure, engaging in derring-do and delicious (but discreet) dalliances, always seeing that justice is done...in sensual secrecy.
name: Steampunk Angels

description: MORTAL COMBAT! Fully embracing his Archangel heritage, Detective Jonah Wright has brutally battled his way through the ancient tournament, EPOCH. Now, finally, he has an opportunity to confront the murderer of his dead partner, Michael, and exact his own brand of justice. Will Jonah triumph and maintain the Angels' benevolent control over the Supernatural Council, or will he become just another body left on the tournament floor?
